fields.text: How would you like your refrigerator to alert you when you're running low on your favorite foods? Or tell you who's ringing your doorbell? With smart home technology, all of these scenarios are possible. If you're interested in investing in this type of technology, it's important to be aware of the pros and cons. Read on to learn more � and to find out if home automation is right for you.
